Coded by user35p74a. 
This program is used to create project folders.
It has to be upgraded so if you see something that isn't perfect. 
usage: 
	makefile [option] [other] | create a makefile with asked values.

options: 
	-h | display help page 
	-l | list all users
	-s | create a makefile with a specified language
	-c | create a makefile with basic attributes
